Third-Party Advertisers
Third-Party Websites and Applications
The Application may contain advertisements from third parties not affiliated with us and which may link to other websites, services, or mobile applications. We cannot guarantee the safety and privacy of data you provide to any third parties. Any data collected by third parties is not covered by this privacy policy.
Data Retention
We will retain your data for as long as you use the Application and for a reasonable time thereafter. We will retain automatically collected information for up to 24 months and thereafter may store it in aggregate.
Our data processing partners will store, process, and delete your data in accordance with their privacy policies and for the duration outlined there.
Information Safety
We have implemented appropriate technical and organizational security measures designed to protect the security of any personal information we process. Please be aware that, although we endeavor provide reasonable security for information we process and maintain, no security system can prevent all potential security breaches. Although we have made our best effort, transmission of personal information to and from our Application, Services, or Support is at your own risk.
Information from Children
This Application, Services, and its Support does not knowingly collect data from or market to anyone under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and are aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact
privacy@inddev.io
.
Privacy Rights
If you are a resident of the EEA, you may review or change your privacy choices at any time within the Application. In version 3.0, navigate to your settings within the Application and select "Manage privacy options."
Updated Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy. The updated version will be indicated with an updated date and the updated version is effective as soon as it is published. If we make material changes to this privacy policy, we will notify you by prominently posting a notice of such changes.
